WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning, family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.190
be with you all again today. I was

00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:06.550
praying and I was asking the Lord. I

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.150
said, 'What do you want me to tell your

00:00:08.150 --> 00:00:08.160
people?'And

00:00:08.160 --> 00:00:10.150
he said, 'Brandon, I want

00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:11.749
you to go back and I want you to tell

00:00:11.759 --> 00:00:14.749
them again about your

00:00:14.749 --> 00:00:14.759
incident

00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:17.109
that happened with your

00:00:17.119 --> 00:00:19.429
dog, with your daughter.'And I said,

00:00:19.439 --> 00:00:21.029
'Okay, well, I can do that.'But it's a

00:00:21.039 --> 00:00:23.349
very hard story for me to tell.

00:00:23.359 --> 00:00:26.150
It's a pride

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:27.910
buster. It's a flesh buster. It's

00:00:27.920 --> 00:00:29.750
everything for me because of how I

00:00:29.760 --> 00:00:32.630
acted. But the Lord wants you to know

00:00:32.640 --> 00:00:35.030
that you don't have to be perfect

00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:38.389
to serve him. You don't have to be

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:40.790
somebody that is walking around like a

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.030
holy angel choir singing behind them all

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:45.670
the time for God to use them. I want you

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:48.470
to understand today that it's all by

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:51.110
grace. And here's what I did. I did

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.670
something really stupid.

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:57.670
My son and I were playing a game.

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:00.470
It was right after Christmas and

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:04.310
we were on Christmas break, and we

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.390
were playing a game online together

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:08.950
and we were just having fun. My

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.109
daughter was playing with the

00:01:11.119 --> 00:01:13.910
puppy that I got her for Christmas, and

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.990
it was a small little dog.

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:18.310
I felt inside before, when

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:20.789
she was playing with this dog, I told her,

00:01:20.799 --> 00:01:22.550
'Honey, you need to put the dog up. I

00:01:22.560 --> 00:01:23.830
don't know, you just need to put the dog

00:01:23.840 --> 00:01:25.670
up. Don't let the dog run around by

00:01:25.680 --> 00:01:27.670
my feet and

00:01:27.670 --> 00:01:27.680
everything,'because

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:28.950
the dog was sitting there nipping at my

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:30.950
toes and was just playing around,

00:01:30.960 --> 00:01:32.550
you know. And so I told my daughter, I

00:01:32.560 --> 00:01:34.149
said, 'You need to put the dog up,

00:01:34.149 --> 00:01:34.159
honey.'And

00:01:34.159 --> 00:01:36.069
so I thought she had

00:01:36.079 --> 00:01:37.910
already obeyed and put the dog up.

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.510
She was sitting there coloring

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:41.749
in her coloring book and was over

00:01:41.759 --> 00:01:43.830
here to my side, but I didn't know that

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:45.910
she had put the dog underneath my feet

00:01:45.920 --> 00:01:49.910
in a blanket. And so I jumped up to go

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:51.350
to the bathroom real quick because I put

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:53.590
the game on pause with my son, and I

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:57.429
jumped up and I landed on that dog and

00:01:57.439 --> 00:02:00.789
I crushed it completely.

00:02:00.799 --> 00:02:03.350
Guts came out the

00:02:03.360 --> 00:02:06.149
side. Blood was coming out the nose.

00:02:06.159 --> 00:02:09.589
The dog was shaking profusely,

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:11.750
and then all of a sudden, I picked up

00:02:11.760 --> 00:02:13.750
the dog and I'm looking at it, and the

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:15.910
dog just died in my hands because

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:20.229
I crushed it. So I lost it. I

00:02:20.239 --> 00:02:23.110
started using bad words. I started

00:02:23.120 --> 00:02:25.030
yelling at my daughter because of what

00:02:25.040 --> 00:02:27.110
she did, putting the dog underneath my

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:30.869
feet. And I just lost it,

00:02:30.879 --> 00:02:32.390
y'all. I'm embarrassed to say

00:02:32.400 --> 00:02:36.070
it, but I lost my temper and I

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:38.309
shouldn't have done it, you know. And so

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:40.309
I was screaming at my little girl for

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:42.470
not obeying me. I was mad at the

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:45.190
situation. Bottom line is, I acted a

00:02:45.200 --> 00:02:47.030
fool. I acted like a total

00:02:47.030 --> 00:02:47.040
you-know-what.

00:02:47.040 --> 00:02:49.030
I shouldn't have done it. And me,

00:02:49.040 --> 00:02:51.270
freaking out, I'm screaming and

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:53.190
yelling, 'Why did this happen? You know,

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:55.990
you should have obeyed and you

00:02:55.990 --> 00:02:56.000
didn't!'And

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.910
I'm mad at my wife. I'm mad at

00:02:57.920 --> 00:02:59.270
everybody. I'm blaming everybody other

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:01.350
than myself for not looking at the dog

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:04.110
below because I acted a fool.

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:07.910
And I'm so upset at the dead dog in

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:09.670
my hand, and I was looking at it as a

00:03:09.680 --> 00:03:13.030
total loss. I mean, it's gone. And so

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:14.869
I'm like, 'You know what? It is what

00:03:14.879 --> 00:03:18.229
it is.'So I freaked out. And

00:03:18.239 --> 00:03:21.589
so I took the dog, and my wife had a

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:25.110
shoe box, and I said, 'Put that dog in

00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:27.270
that shoe box and put it out on the

00:03:27.280 --> 00:03:28.949
porch. I don't want to deal with

00:03:28.949 --> 00:03:28.959
it.'It

00:03:28.959 --> 00:03:30.949
was because it was cold, and here in

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:32.630
Oklahoma, it gets really cold and the

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:34.309
ground was frozen, and I knew that there

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:35.830
was no way I could dig a hole in the

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.190
middle of the night. It

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:39.350
just had snowed and it was freezing

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:41.350
cold. So I said, 'Put the dog in the

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:42.869
shoe box and put it on the porch. I

00:03:42.879 --> 00:03:44.309
don't want to deal with it right

00:03:44.309 --> 00:03:44.319
now.'And

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:46.390
so my little girl turned to me

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.670
and she said, 'Daddy, aren't you going

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:49.270
to pray for it to be raised from the

00:03:49.270 --> 00:03:49.280
dead?'And

00:03:49.280 --> 00:03:51.830
I said, 'Honey,

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:53.830
God's not going to hear me when I pray

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.670
right now for that dog to be raised. You

00:03:55.670 --> 00:03:55.680
pray.'I

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:58.229
said, 'I'm not

00:03:58.239 --> 00:04:00.630
there. You pray.'She said, 'All things are possible to him who believes,'like that to me. I told her, 'I'm not there.

00:04:22.320 --> 00:04:25.510
I just acted out, and the

00:04:25.520 --> 00:04:27.629
Lord's not going to hear me when I

00:04:27.639 --> 00:04:30.710
pray. You pray.'So, she

00:04:30.720 --> 00:04:32.590
started marching up and down the

00:04:32.600 --> 00:04:35.270
hall, just saying, 'All things are

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:38.070
possible to him that believes.'And at

00:04:38.080 --> 00:04:41.030
this time, I left the room because I was

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:43.550
so angry. I had to get some

00:04:43.560 --> 00:04:46.550
space. So, I went into our bedroom and I

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:48.390
shut the door and I prayed. I asked

00:04:48.390 --> 00:04:48.400
God—because

00:04:48.400 --> 00:04:50.469
I lost it so

00:04:50.479 --> 00:04:52.550
bad. And I could hear my little girl up

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:55.030
and down the hall, 'In the name of Jesus,

00:04:55.040 --> 00:04:56.629
get up from the dead! In the name of

00:04:56.639 --> 00:04:58.469
Jesus, get up from the

00:04:58.469 --> 00:04:58.479
dead!'And

00:04:58.479 --> 00:05:00.230
needless to say, that dog was dead in

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:02.950
that box. My wife had put it outside

00:05:02.960 --> 00:05:05.030
in the cold. It was completely cold

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:07.430
outside and everything was frozen. And

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:08.870
I told her to put it in

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.469
the trash can or whatever, and I would

00:05:10.479 --> 00:05:13.909
deal with it in the morning. Well, I was

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:16.230
praying, and all of a sudden, an hour goes

00:05:16.240 --> 00:05:19.590
by, two hours go by, and I come back

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:21.110
in and I make amends with the family.

00:05:21.120 --> 00:05:22.790
And I told them, 'I'm sorry. I

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.950
just acted a fool. I

00:05:24.960 --> 00:05:26.950
acted out of anger. It was

00:05:26.960 --> 00:05:28.710
all based out of fear. I was afraid of

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:30.150
the loss, afraid of everything. I was

00:05:30.160 --> 00:05:31.590
blaming myself, I was blaming you, and

00:05:31.600 --> 00:05:32.870
the way I handled it, I'm sorry.'And I

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.070
apologized, you know, and I took

00:05:34.080 --> 00:05:36.390
communion over it, and I put

00:05:36.400 --> 00:05:38.629
it at the foot of Jesus. That's where I

00:05:38.639 --> 00:05:41.029
was. My little girl was still crying,

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:43.029
still upset. I was holding her at

00:05:43.039 --> 00:05:45.110
that time, 'Baby, I'm sorry I

00:05:45.120 --> 00:05:46.469
yelled at you and freaked out

00:05:46.479 --> 00:05:48.390
at the situation. I'm sorry you

00:05:48.400 --> 00:05:51.189
lost your dog. We'll replace him. But

00:05:51.199 --> 00:05:53.110
God's got this, you know.'And

00:05:53.110 --> 00:05:53.120
I was

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:54.950
just trying to comfort her, comfort the

00:05:54.960 --> 00:05:57.070
family because of my actions and

00:05:57.080 --> 00:06:01.749
everything. So, my wife goes,

00:06:01.759 --> 00:06:03.189
like I said, this is about two

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:07.350
hours later. She goes to take the

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:09.830
trash out, and I hear her say, 'The

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:11.909
dog's gone. It wasn't in the shoe box

00:06:11.909 --> 00:06:11.919
anymore.'So,

00:06:11.919 --> 00:06:14.469
I thought the raccoons

00:06:14.479 --> 00:06:17.189
had gotten the dog. And so, you know,

00:06:17.199 --> 00:06:18.469
I'm sitting there, and all of a sudden,

00:06:18.479 --> 00:06:21.350
she says, 'I hear a squeaking

00:06:21.350 --> 00:06:21.360
noise.'And

00:06:21.360 --> 00:06:22.870
it was like, 'Squeak,

00:06:22.870 --> 00:06:22.880
squeak.'She

00:06:22.880 --> 00:06:24.230
said, 'I hear a squeaking

00:06:24.230 --> 00:06:24.240
noise.'She

00:06:24.240 --> 00:06:26.150
starts looking

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:30.150
down, and she sees the dog at the bottom

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:34.150
of the trash can, alive, completely

00:06:34.160 --> 00:06:37.110
alive, begging, wagging its tail,

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:40.870
begging to get out of that trash can.

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:42.790
She goes and tips the trash can over,

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:46.230
grabs that dog, and pulls it out. God

00:06:46.240 --> 00:06:49.230
had completely

00:06:49.240 --> 00:06:52.270
restored all that dog's guts back

00:06:52.280 --> 00:06:55.189
inside. The blood was completely wiped

00:06:55.199 --> 00:06:58.870
off of it. There were no signs of any

00:06:58.880 --> 00:07:03.270
kind of trauma on this dog at all.

00:07:03.280 --> 00:07:05.749
God had completely done a creative

00:07:05.759 --> 00:07:07.710
miracle on that

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:10.469
dog. And my wife brought that little

00:07:10.479 --> 00:07:13.029
puppy in, and it was shivering cold

00:07:13.039 --> 00:07:15.110
because it was freezing, which is a

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:17.390
miracle in itself because of how cold it

00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:20.710
was. And the dog was shaking. And so we

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:23.510
put a blow dryer on the dog and started

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:25.830
heating that dog up. And my little girl

00:07:25.840 --> 00:07:28.309
was screaming, 'I told you all things

00:07:28.319 --> 00:07:31.350
are possible to him that believes! I

00:07:31.360 --> 00:07:34.550
told you all things are possible to him

00:07:34.560 --> 00:07:36.309
that believes, Daddy! I told you he

00:07:36.319 --> 00:07:37.830
would bring him back! I told you he'd

00:07:37.840 --> 00:07:39.749
bring him back!'because I trained my children

00:07:39.759 --> 00:07:41.469
to believe the

00:07:41.479 --> 00:07:43.830
impossible. I trained my children

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:46.950
to believe that Jesus is

00:07:46.960 --> 00:07:50.150
the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:07:50.160 --> 00:07:52.469
And the same Jesus that healed the sick

00:07:52.479 --> 00:07:55.990
2,000 years ago even cares about a dog

00:07:56.000 --> 00:07:59.510
that dies in the bottom of a trash can.

00:07:59.520 --> 00:08:02.550
He will even touch your dog. He's no respecter

00:08:02.550 --> 00:08:02.560
of persons.

00:08:02.560 --> 00:08:05.189
I believe with all

00:08:05.199 --> 00:08:07.510
my heart that the faith of a mustard

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:09.830
seed can move a mountain. I believe even

00:08:09.840 --> 00:08:13.510
a childlike faith can bring a dog back.

00:08:13.520 --> 00:08:18.029
All things are possible to him who will

00:08:18.039 --> 00:08:20.309
believe. And that's what He did

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:22.710
that day for her.

00:08:22.720 --> 00:08:24.469
She came down that hall and she's loving

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:26.150
that little dog and she's holding it in

00:08:26.150 --> 00:08:26.160
her

00:08:26.160 --> 00:08:29.029
hands and she was saying, 'Daddy, I

00:08:29.039 --> 00:08:31.830
told you all things are possible to him

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:33.269
who believes.'And she kept saying it

00:08:33.279 --> 00:08:35.750
over and over again, just rejoicing

00:08:35.760 --> 00:08:37.750
and loving that dog and lifting it up in

00:08:37.760 --> 00:08:39.509
the air and rejoicing because of what

00:08:39.519 --> 00:08:42.230
God had just done for her. When my wife

00:08:42.240 --> 00:08:45.269
brought that dog in and it was

00:08:45.269 --> 00:08:45.279
complete—no

00:08:45.279 --> 00:08:47.389
guts, no blood, no nothing out of his

00:08:47.399 --> 00:08:50.949
nose, all bones restored, walking around

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:54.070
like normal again, all of it completely

00:08:54.080 --> 00:08:56.110
like nothing had ever

00:08:56.110 --> 00:08:56.120
happened—it

00:08:56.120 --> 00:08:58.870
was like a holy hush in my

00:08:58.880 --> 00:09:01.590
house. The presence of the Lord was so

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:03.630
strong, and you could feel

00:09:03.640 --> 00:09:06.389
it. But this is what I want to say to

00:09:06.399 --> 00:09:09.190
you. I had it in my heart, and the Lord

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.949
told me, and I'll say it again

00:09:10.959 --> 00:09:13.590
to you all. The Lord

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:17.269
said this to me: 'Brandon, even on

00:09:17.279 --> 00:09:19.590
your best day'—because I thought in my mind,

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:21.269
this is what I thought, 'Man,

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:23.190
if I would have

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:24.389
prayed for it, or

00:09:24.389 --> 00:09:24.399
whatever,'making

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:26.150
all

00:09:26.160 --> 00:09:28.310
these excuses up in my head and

00:09:28.320 --> 00:09:30.150
talking to him about everything, and

00:09:30.160 --> 00:09:32.470
I was like, 'Wow!'And he stopped me

00:09:32.480 --> 00:09:34.230
and he corrected me

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:35.750
immediately. He said this to me:

00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:39.670
'Brandon, even on your best day, son,

00:09:39.680 --> 00:09:42.030
your righteousness is as filthy rags to

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:44.430
me. Even on your best

00:09:44.440 --> 00:09:48.630
day, you cannot earn the anointing. You

00:09:48.640 --> 00:09:51.829
cannot earn your salvation. You

00:09:51.839 --> 00:09:55.430
cannot earn healing. It's all by grace.

00:09:55.440 --> 00:09:57.990
I paid the price for you for all of it.

00:09:58.000 --> 00:09:59.990
And I raised that dog up as a sign

00:09:59.990 --> 00:10:00.000
and

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:02.150
wonder to your little

00:10:02.150 --> 00:10:02.160
girl.'Do

00:10:02.160 --> 00:10:04.790
you get that, y'all? He brought the dog

00:10:04.800 --> 00:10:07.590
back, and he did it just for a child. And

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:09.269
that's what I'm trying to tell you. She

00:10:09.279 --> 00:10:10.389
was down there, and she prayed.

00:10:10.399 --> 00:10:11.670
Like I said, that's

00:10:11.680 --> 00:10:13.269
the way we raise our children. We

00:10:13.279 --> 00:10:15.590
believe with all our heart that Jesus

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:18.670
Christ is still doing miracles

00:10:18.680 --> 00:10:22.110
today. And I just want to tell you all,

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:26.230
people are always asking me

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:28.470
about my faith walk and

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:29.910
everything, and I just want to tell

00:10:29.920 --> 00:10:31.990
you I'm just normal. I'm just a normal

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:33.590
human being. I've got issues just like

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:36.069
everybody else. I'm a work in progress.

00:10:36.079 --> 00:10:39.110
I take one day at a time, and I seek

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:42.230
his face every single day. I seek him

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:44.630
for finances, I seek

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:47.030
him to provide for my family as

00:10:47.030 --> 00:10:47.040
the

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:49.670
head of my house, and for better jobs.

00:10:49.680 --> 00:10:52.069
I pray that over us: 'Father, increase

00:10:52.079 --> 00:10:53.990
our hands so we can be a blessing to

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:55.990
your people.'You can't be a real

00:10:56.000 --> 00:10:57.590
blessing a lot of times if you're

00:10:57.600 --> 00:10:58.710
broke and making it from

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:01.030
paycheck to paycheck, only

00:11:01.030 --> 00:11:01.040
having

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:02.550
enough to pay your bills and

00:11:02.550 --> 00:11:02.560
borrowing

00:11:02.560 --> 00:11:04.790
the rest. So that's where I'm

00:11:04.800 --> 00:11:07.430
at. I'm always believing for

00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:09.269
the supernatural. I'm always believing

00:11:09.279 --> 00:11:11.910
